# --- harness dogfooding state (machine-specific) ---
# harness generates these from YOUR selection and personal shared library
# (~/.harness), so they are not portable across contributors. Run `harness`
# to regenerate them locally. See CONTRIBUTING.md.
/harness.yaml
/AGENTS.md

# --- Project-local agent artifacts ---
# Vendored or localized copies of shared / third-party artifacts must NOT be
# committed here — only artifacts native to harness's own development are kept
# (the dev rule below and the specs under .agents/specs/). Everything else that
# lands under the kind containers is ignored. See CONTRIBUTING.md.
/.agents/skills/
/.agents/agents/
/.agents/mcps/
/.agents/rules/*
!/.agents/rules/go-code-standards/
